WEBVTT

00:01.502 --> 00:02.742
<i>Previously on "bates motel"...</i>

00:02.836 --> 00:04.503
Do you think maybe
we could be friends?

00:04.604 --> 00:05.738
Of course.

00:05.839 --> 00:07.119
Like, we could
hang out sometime?

00:07.207 --> 00:08.940
I mean, even though I'm married?

00:09.043 --> 00:10.742
Holy shit.

00:10.845 --> 00:12.010
Well, now you know, chick.

00:12.113 --> 00:14.012
Can you keep this secret
about me?

00:14.114 --> 00:15.247
Can I trust you, chick?

00:15.348 --> 00:16.415
Hey, norma?

00:16.516 --> 00:18.416
Can I stay here
for a little while?

00:18.518 --> 00:19.851
Oof!

00:19.954 --> 00:21.452
Back up. Back up.

00:21.555 --> 00:23.588
What are you doing?
You trying to steal our car?

00:23.690 --> 00:25.130
You don't need to do it.
I'll just...

00:26.626 --> 00:27.860
Mother?

00:27.961 --> 00:29.006
I need you to do
something for me.

00:29.030 --> 00:30.195
<i>I need you to kill him.</i>

00:30.297 --> 00:31.463
I want you to leave.

00:31.565 --> 00:32.463
And never come back.

00:32.567 --> 00:33.865
Go!

00:33.968 --> 00:35.433
<i>Go! - Norman!</i>

00:35.569 --> 00:37.203
He will ruin us!

00:40.207 --> 00:41.873
Hey!

